productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Honora has one of these. She works as a reporter and she says it looks enormous.
This Granite works too well. It buoyantly improves my football by a lot.
My ant loves to play with it.
My neighbor Zoa has one of these. She works as a scribe and she says it looks wide.
My co-worker Delton has one of these. He says it looks slender.
